description: The contract covers the replacement of an AOSTON tower of a light house at the site known as "LL491 - Scotch Bonnet Island". The existing abandoned light house station has historical significance and is to be maintained in its present condition. Intention is to remove the existing AOSTON and construct the new tower in the same location. The new tower has been fabricated by others in anticipation of construction and will be provided to the Contractor at the CCG DSL.Duration of contract:(2023-03-22) to (2023-06-30)Time frame of delivery:(2023-03-22) to (2023-06-30)
